OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, In the very first days of this invasion
OL,6, a 62-year-old unarmed civilian was shot
OL,7, dead on a village street outside his   
OL,8, Ukrainian home. His name was Oleksandr 
OL,9, Shelipov.                              
OL,11,FThree months later and the captured    
OL,12,FRussian soldier accused of killing him 
OL,13,Fis in Kyiv being tried for a war crime.
OL,15,FStanding up in court to confront the   
OL,16,F21-year-old defendant on Thursday was  
OL,17,FKateryna Shelipova, the widow of the   
OL,18,Fman killed.                            
OL,20,FDid he repent his crime, she asked?    
